description: Ministry of City Planning and Water Supply - Orders made to approve the acquisition of the immovable properties in Kandewatta, Galle Four Gravets D/S Division, Galle District for the constructions under Galle Municipal Boundaries Wastewater Recycling Project and in Arukalmadam, Nallur D/S Division, Jaffna District for the constructions of Swerage Pump House No. 16 and in Oddumadam, Jaffna D/S Division, Jaffna District  for the constructions of Sewerage Pump House, NO. 25 under the Jaffna-Kilinochchi Water Supply & Sanitation Project
